# 1. Make a copy of this file in the SAME folder and name the copy ".env"
#      Mac / Anaconda Prompt:  cp .env.example .env
#      Windows (cmd):          copy .env.example .env
#    (Or just duplicate the file and rename it to ".env".)
# 2. Get a free Gemini API key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# 3. In your new ".env" file, replace your_gemini_api_key_here with your real key, then save.
# ⚠️ Your ".env" is private — never share it or post it online. (Only THIS .env.example is shared.)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
